            <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 shadow-sm mb-10">
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-4">A. What is a 2-Dimensional Array?</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mb-4"><strong>Definition:</strong> A 2-Dimensional (2D) array is an array within an array. It is structured like a table or a grid consisting of rows and columns.</p>
                
                <div class="flex items-start gap-4 bg-purple-50 border border-purple-100 p-5 rounded-2xl shadow-sm mb-4">
