                <p class="text-xs text-emerald-700 bg-emerald-50 p-2 rounded inline-block"><strong><i class="fa-solid fa-satellite-dish mr-1"></i> Importance in IoT:</strong> Used to store coordinate mapping data or pixel data for a camera module.</p>
