                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-amber-400 mb-6 relative z-10">B. Python Program to Generate a 2D Array <span class="bg-red-500 text-white text-[10px] px-2 py-0.5 rounded uppercase tracking-wider ml-2 align-middle shadow-sm">PYQ</span></h3>
                <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm mb-6 relative z-10">This program asks the user for the number of rows (m) and columns (n), and fills the 2D array with <code>row &times; col</code> multiplication values.</p>

                <div class="bg-black/60 rounded-xl p-5 shadow-inner font-mono text-sm code-block border-l-4 border-l-amber-400 relative z-10">
                    <span class="text-slate-400"># Take input for rows (m) and columns (n)</span><br/>
                    <span class="text-sky-300">m</span> = <span class="text-emerald-300">int</span>(<span class="text-emerald-300">input</span>(<span class="text-amber-300">"Enter number of rows (m): "</span>))<br/>
                    <span class="text-sky-300">n</span> = <span class="text-emerald-300">int</span>(<span class="text-emerald-300">input</span>(<span class="text-amber-300">"Enter number of columns (n): "</span>))<br/><br/>

                    <span class="text-slate-400"># Create an empty 2D array</span><br/>
